-- Commercial Bank of Africa Raises Funds for Expansion, Daily Says
-- B y   E r i c   O m b o k
-- 2012-08-14T04:01:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-14/commercial-bank-of-africa-raises-funds-for-expansion-daily-says.html
Commercial Bank of Africa Ltd. has
raised 1.5 billion shillings ($18 million) from holders through
a private placement, Business Daily said citing Group Chief
Executive Officer Isaac Awuondo.  The Kenyan lender, which has operations in Tanzania, will
use the funds to expand into neighbouring Uganda upon approval
of its license, the Nairobi-based newspaper said. Commercial
Bank also intends to expand into Rwanda and Burundi next year,
it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eric Ombok in Nairobi at 
 eombok@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
